Deputies to 15th-term Hanchongryon Meet 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, February 17 (KCNA) -- A meeting of the deputies to the 15th-term south Korean Federation of University Student Councils (Hanchongryon) was reportedly held in Seoul on Feb. 11. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
