 The meeting stressed the need to intensify the actions against the U.S., war and the Grand National Party of south Korea (GNP) and the struggle for the withdrawal of the U.S. troops, the repeal of the "National Security Law" and the lifting of the enemy-benefiting label from Hanchongryon and dynamically wage the movement for implementing the June 15 joint declaration this year. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
