 A special statement made public at the meeting termed 2007 a year of confrontation with the U.S. and outside forces to put an end to outside forces' colonial rule and subjugation and bring about a turning phase for national reunification and a year of the struggle for protecting peace against war and for the great unity of the nation. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It said that the U.S. is watching for a chance to ignite a war in this land and the GNP is keen on the pro-U.S. moves against the north and working hard to grab power through the "presidential elections" this year at any cost in a bid to revive the era of fascism and confrontation with the north. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The 15th-term Hanchongryon will make a general advance to emerge victorious in the struggle against the U.S., war and the GNP and play its honorable role as vanguard ushering in a heyday of independent reunification of the country, the statement stressed.

